## Frontend Architecture (web-src/)

### **Feature-First with Infrastructure Separation**

**Business features organized Feature-First, infrastructure separated for reuse:**

```text
web-src/src/
├── features/                    # Business capabilities (Feature-First DDD)
│   ├── products/               # Complete product feature capabilities
│   │   ├── export-ui.js        # Product export UI workflows
│   │   ├── export-ui.css       # Feature-specific styling
│   │   └── shared/             # Cross-export utilities
│   ├── files/                  # Complete file feature capabilities
│   │   ├── browser-ui.js       # File browser UI workflows
│   │   ├── browser-ui.css      # Feature-specific styling
│   │   ├── upload-ui.js        # File upload UI workflows
│   │   ├── download-ui.js      # File download UI workflows
│   │   └── shared/             # Cross-file utilities
│   └── commerce/               # Commerce feature capabilities
│       ├── auth-ui.js          # Authentication workflows
│       └── shared/             # Commerce UI utilities
├── infrastructure/             # Technical concerns (NOT business features)
│   ├── components/             # Reusable UI primitives
│   │   ├── button/             # Button component
│   │   ├── modal/              # Modal component
│   │   ├── notification/       # Notification system
│   │   └── form/               # Form components
│   ├── design-system/          # Visual design system
│   │   ├── tokens.css          # Design tokens
│   │   ├── utilities.css       # CSS utilities
│   │   └── layout.css          # Layout patterns
│   └── core/                   # Cross-feature infrastructure
│       ├── config/             # Configuration management
│       ├── url/                # URL building
│       ├── htmx/               # HTMX setup and events
│       └── utils/              # Universal utilities
└── main.js                     # Application initialization
```

### **Frontend Feature Pattern**

```javascript
// features/products/export-ui.js
/**
 * Products Export UI
 * Complete product export user interface capability
 */

// Infrastructure dependencies (clear from paths)
import { showNotification } from '../../infrastructure/components/notification/index.js';
import { getActionUrl } from '../../infrastructure/core/url/index.js';
import { Button } from '../../infrastructure/components/button/index.js';

// === EXPORT UI WORKFLOWS === (What users interact with)
export function initializeProductExport() {
  // Step 1: Setup export form handling
  setupExportFormHandling();
  
  // Step 2: Initialize progress tracking
  initializeExportProgress();
  
  // Step 3: Setup result handling
  setupExportResultHandling();
}

// === EXPORT UI OPERATIONS === (UI coordination logic)
function setupExportFormHandling() {
  // Export form handling logic
}

function initializeExportProgress() {
  // Progress tracking logic
}

// === EXPORT UI UTILITIES === (Building blocks)
function showExportStartNotification() {
  showNotification('Export started...', 'info');
}
```

### **HTMX Progressive Enhancement**

**Server-side templates with frontend enhancement:**

```javascript
// Backend: src/htmx/file-browser-ui.js generates HTML templates
// Frontend: features/files/browser-ui.js adds progressive enhancement

// Progressive enhancement pattern
document.addEventListener('htmx:afterSwap', (event) => {
  if (event.target.matches('[data-feature="file-browser"]')) {
    enhanceFileBrowserInteractions(event.target);
  }
});

function enhanceFileBrowserInteractions(container) {
  // Add drag-and-drop functionality
  // Add keyboard navigation
  // Add client-side validation
}
```

### **Frontend Configuration**

**Auto-generated configuration from backend:**

```javascript
// Infrastructure: Generated at build time from backend config
// infrastructure/core/config/index.js (auto-generated)
export const getTimeout = () => 30000;
export const getActionUrl = (action, params) => {
  // Generated URL building logic
};

// Features: Use infrastructure configuration
import { getTimeout, getActionUrl } from '../../infrastructure/core/config/index.js';

// Configure HTMX with backend-generated settings
htmx.config.timeout = getTimeout();
```

